databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select country_code as country_code_mailing,state_id as state_id_mailing ,addressline1 as addressline1_mailing ,addressline2 as addressline2_mailing,city as city_mailing,zip as zip_mailing,phone as phone_mailing,fax as fax_mailing,po_box as po_box_mailing,extn,county as county_mailing,e_mail as e_mail_mailing from tbl_address where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid# and type=3 and person_id is null

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyListPublicSubmitW9AddrerssInfo
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select ta.country_code as country_code_w9,state_id as state_id_w9,addressline1 as addressline1_w9,addressline2 as addressline2_w9,city as city_w9,zip as zip_w9,phone as phone_w9,fax as fax_w9,po_box as po_box_w9,ta.extn as extn_mailing ,county as county_mailing,e_mail as e_mail_w9,county as county_w9,taxpayer_name AS w9_legal_name from tbl_address ta inner join tbl_agencyappointmentrequest aar WITH(NOLOCK) ON ta.aar_requestid = aar.aar_requestid where ta.aar_requestid=#aar_requestid# and type=2 and person_id is null

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyListPublicSubmitDECAddressInfo
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: SELECT state_id as state_id_DEC,addressline1 as addressline1_DEC,addressline2 as addressline2_DEC,city as city_DEC,county as county_DEC,zip as zip_DEC,phone as phone_DEC,fax as fax_DEC,e_mail as e_mail_DEC,extn as extn_DEC,country_code as country_code_DEC,territory_id as territory_id_DEC,agency_zip_code_2 as agency_zip_code_2_DEC,agency_foreign_addr_in as agency_foreign_addr_in_DEC,po_box as po_box_DEC,alt_phone as alt_phone_DEC,alt_extn as alt_extn_DEC ,addressline3 as addressline3_DEC ,alt_email as alt_email_DEC from tbl_address where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid# AND type=5 AND person_id IS NULL

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyReviewQuestionsData
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select top 1 learn_about,interest_in_other_business,interest_for_appointment,agency_experience,agency_financials,perpetuation_plan,marketing_plan,location_of_agency,other_companies_representated,agency_brief_profile from tbl_agency_review where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getSocialMediaInfoQuery
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select sms.code as tbl_social_media_site, social_media_agency_id ,social_media_user_id as social_media_userid,social_media_id ,smi.id ,sms.description as social_media_site_desc, ROW_NUMBER() over(order by smi.id asc) as rownum from tbl_social_media_info smi inner join social_media_sites sms on sms.id = smi.social_media_id where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: chkOtherAgencyLocation
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select master_lookup_data_code from master_lookup_data_lku where master_lookup_data_id =#agency_location#

databaseoperation.name: getAppointmentRequestData
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select b.master_lookup_data_desc as entity_type,*,dbo.getAmountFormat(agency_volume) as 'agencyvolume' ,dbo.getAmountFormat(aar_mkttotpremium) as 'marketpremium' ,(select description from producertype_lku where prdcrtype_id=ta.aar_producertypeid) as 'legaldescription' ,(select b.master_lookup_data_desc as agency_comparativerate_desc from master_lookup_detail_lku a inner join dbo.master_lookup_data_lku b on a.master_lookup_detail_id = b.master_lookup_detail_id where b.master_lookup_data_id=ta.agency_management_system ) as agency_management_system_desc ,stuff((select ', ' + b.master_lookup_data_desc from tbl_agencyappointmentrequest ta left join dbo.master_lookup_data_lku b on b.master_lookup_data_id in (select items from dbo.split(ta.agency_comparativerate,',')) left join master_lookup_detail_lku a on a.master_lookup_detail_id = b.master_lookup_detail_id where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid# for xml path('')),1,1,'') as agency_comparativerate_pdf from tbl_agencyappointmentrequest ta left join dbo.master_lookup_data_lku b on b.master_lookup_data_id= ta.entity_type left join master_lookup_detail_lku a on a.master_lookup_detail_id = b.master_lookup_detail_id where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getMarketInformationData
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select case when aar_carrierid=-1 then aar_carrier else (select description from carrier_lku where carrier_id=aar_carrierid) end as aar_carrier, (select description from lob_lku where lob_id=aar_lobid) as market_lob,loss_ratio,commissionrate, dbo.getAmountFormat(writtenpremium) as writtenpremium,retentionrate from tbl_marketinformation where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyQuestionsList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select a.questionid,bg.question,a.response,a.comment,case when isnull(a.comment,'')!='' then 'Y' else 'N' end as showComment from tbl_agencyquestions a,backgroundquestions_lku bg where a.questionid=bg.questionid and a.aar_requestid=#aar_requestid# union select questionid,question,0 as response,null as comment, 'N' as showComments from backgroundquestions_lku bg where bg.questionid not in(select questionid from tbl_agencyquestions where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#) and bg_question_type=1

databaseoperation.name: getStatesData
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select cast(substring((select ', '+description from state_lku where state_id in(select items from dbo.Split((select state_ids from tbl_appointmentstates where request_id=#aar_requestid#),','))order by description asc for xml path('')),2,8000) as varchar(8000)) as states

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyBusinessAddress
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select cntry.country_code as aar_country_code,extn as aar_extn,address_id as aar_address_id, sl.state_id as aar_state, addressline1 as aar_streetaddress1, addressline2 as aar_streetaddress2, city as aar_city, case when zip is not null then case when datalength(zip) = 9 then substring(zip,1,5) + '-' + substring(zip,6,9) else zip end else zip end as aar_zipcode, case when phone is not null then substring(phone,1,3) + '-' + substring(phone,4,3) + '-' + substring(phone,7,4) else phone end as aar_phoneno, case when fax is not null then substring(fax,1,3) + '-' + substring(fax,4,3) + '-' + substring(fax,7,4) else fax end as aar_fax, type,e_mail as aar_email, case when mobile is not null then substring(mobile,1,3) + '-' + substring(mobile,4,3) + '-' + substring(mobile,7,4) else mobile end as aar_mobile, cntry.territory_id,sl.description as aar_stateDescription,cntry.country_name as aar_countryDescription,county.description as aar_countyDescription, case when alt_phone is not null then substring(alt_phone,1,3) + '-' + substring(alt_phone,4,3) + '-' + substring(alt_phone,7,4) else alt_phone end as aar_altPhone, alt_extn as aar_altExtn,po_box as aar_poBox,adr.agency_zip_code_2,adr.agency_foreign_addr_in,addressline3 from tbl_address adr left outer join state_lku sl on sl.state_id = adr.state_id left outer join country_lku cntry on cntry.country_code = adr.country_code left outer join county_lku county on county.county_id = adr.county where aar_requestid = #aar_requestid# and type = 1 and person_id is null

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyW9Address
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select cntry.country_code as aar_country_code_w9,adr.extn as aar_extn_w9,address_id as aar_address_id_w9, sl.state_id as aar_state_w9, addressline1 as aar_streetaddress1_w9, addressline2 as aar_streetaddress2_w9, city as aar_city_w9, case when zip is not null then case when datalength(zip) = 9 then substring(zip,1,5) + '-' + substring(zip,6,9) else zip end else zip end as aar_zipcode_w9, case when phone is not null then substring(phone,1,3) + '-' + substring(phone,4,3) + '-' + substring(phone,7,4) else phone end as aar_phoneno_w9, case when fax is not null then substring(fax,1,3) + '-' + substring(fax,4,3) + '-' + substring(fax,7,4) else fax end as aar_fax_w9, type,e_mail as aar_email_w9, case when adr.mobile is not null then substring(adr.mobile,1,3) + '-' + substring(adr.mobile,4,3) + '-' + substring(adr.mobile,7,4) else adr.mobile end as aar_mobile_w9, cntry.territory_id as territory_id_w9,sl.description as aar_stateDescription_w9,cntry.country_name as aar_countryDescription_w9,county.description as aar_countyDescription_w9, case when alt_phone is not null then substring(alt_phone,1,3) + '-' + substring(alt_phone,4,3) + '-' + substring(alt_phone,7,4) else alt_phone end as aar_altPhone_w9, alt_extn as aar_altExtn_w9,po_box as aar_poBox_w9,adr.agency_zip_code_2 as agency_zip_code_2_w9,adr.agency_foreign_addr_in as agency_foreign_addr_in_w9,addressline3 as addressline3_w9 , tdf.w9_legal_name from tbl_address adr left outer join state_lku sl on sl.state_id = adr.state_id left outer join country_lku cntry on cntry.country_code = adr.country_code left outer join county_lku county on county.county_id = adr.county left outer join tbl_agencyappointmentrequest tdf on tdf.aar_requestid = adr.aar_requestid where adr.aar_requestid = #aar_requestid# and type = 3 and person_id is null

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyMailingAddress
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select cntry.country_code as aar_country_code_ma,extn as aar_extn_ma,address_id as aar_address_id_ma, sl.state_id as aar_state_ma, addressline1 as aar_streetaddress1_ma, addressline2 as aar_streetaddress2_ma, city as aar_city_ma, case when zip is not null then case when datalength(zip) = 9 then substring(zip,1,5) + '-' + substring(zip,6,9) else zip end else zip end as aar_zipcode_ma, case when phone is not null then substring(phone,1,3) + '-' + substring(phone,4,3) + '-' + substring(phone,7,4) else phone end as aar_phoneno_ma, case when fax is not null then substring(fax,1,3) + '-' + substring(fax,4,3) + '-' + substring(fax,7,4) else fax end as aar_fax_ma, type,e_mail as aar_email_ma, case when mobile is not null then substring(mobile,1,3) + '-' + substring(mobile,4,3) + '-' + substring(mobile,7,4) else mobile end as aar_mobile_ma, cntry.territory_id as territory_id_ma,sl.description as aar_stateDescription_ma,cntry.country_name as aar_countryDescription_ma,county.description as aar_countyDescription_ma, case when alt_phone is not null then substring(alt_phone,1,3) + '-' + substring(alt_phone,4,3) + '-' + substring(alt_phone,7,4) else alt_phone end as aar_altPhone_ma, alt_extn as aar_altExtn_ma,po_box as aar_poBox_ma,adr.agency_zip_code_2 as agency_zip_code_2_ma,adr.agency_foreign_addr_in as agency_foreign_addr_in_ma,addressline3 as addressline3_ma from tbl_address adr left outer join state_lku sl on sl.state_id = adr.state_id left outer join country_lku cntry on cntry.country_code = adr.country_code left outer join county_lku county on county.county_id = adr.county where aar_requestid = #aar_requestid# and type = 2 and person_id is null

databaseoperation.name: getMarketInformationList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select row_number() over(order by marketinformation_id) rownum,case when aar_carrierid = -1 then other_company_description else (select description from carrier_lku where carrier_id=aar_carrierid) end as aar_carrierid_desc, (select description from tbl_lob_lku where lob_id=aar_lobid) as lob_desc, marketinformation_id, case when loss_ratio is null or loss_ratio='' then '' else loss_ratio end as loss_ratio ,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(class1volume as numeric(15,0))) as class1volume,dateofappointment,years_represented, convert(varchar(20),dateofappointment,101) as dateofappointmentFormatted,aar_carrierid,aar_requestid ,yearofappointment from tbl_marketinformation where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getDocumentsData
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select ad.document_id,ad.document_name,doc.document_display_value as document_type,ada.document_name as file_name from tbl_agency_documents ad inner join tbl_agency_document_attachments ada on ad.document_id = ada.object_id inner join document_type_lku doc on doc.document_id = ad.document_type_id where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getEODeclarationList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select carrier_other,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(policy_limit as numeric(16,0))) as policy_limit,effective_date,case eo_claims when 1 then 'Yes' else 'No' end as eo_claims,eoclaims_comments,coverage_amount,expiration_date,policy_number from tbl_agencyappointmentrequest where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getSignatureAcceptanceDetail
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select name,title,email,date,case is_checked when 'Y' then 'Y' else 'N' end as is_checked,case is_checked1 when 'Y' then 'Y' else 'N' end as is_checked1 from tbl_signature_acceptance where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyAssociationCheckBoxValues
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select agency_association,cast((select stuff((select ', ' + master_lookup_data_code from master_lookup_data_lku where master_lookup_data_id in(select items from dbo.split(agency_association,',')) for xml path('')),1,1,'')) as varchar(8000)) as 'agency_association_pdf' from tbl_agencyappointmentrequest where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyComparativeValues
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select agency_comparativerate,cast((select stuff((select ', ' + master_lookup_data_desc from master_lookup_data_lku where master_lookup_data_id in(select items from dbo.split(agency_comparativerate,',')) for xml path('')),1,1,'')) as varchar(8000)) as 'agency_comparativerate_pdf' from tbl_agencyappointmentrequest where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getCyberLiabilityDeclarationList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select carrier_other as cyber_liability_carrier_other,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(policy_limit as numeric(16,0))) as cyber_liability_policy_limit,effective_date as cyber_liability_effective_date, expiration_date as cyber_liability_expiration_date, case cyber_liability_claims when 1 then 'Yes' else 'No' end as cyber_liability_claims,comments as cyber_liability_claims_comments from tbl_agency_cyber_liability where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getPersonalInformationList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select row_number() over(order by personalinformation_id) rownum,personalinformation_id,aar_requestid,name,company,address,phone,relationship,last_updated_by,last_updated_ts from tbl_agencypersonalinformation where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyTerminatedList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select row_number() over(order by agencyterminated_id) rownum,agencyterminated_id,aar_requestid,company_name ,dbo.getAmountFormat(annual_premium_volume) as annual_premium_volume ,date_closed,convert(varchar(20),date_closed,101) as dateClosedFormatted,reason_for_action_taken, case when reason_for_action_taken='0' then 'Low Production' else case when reason_for_action_taken='1' then 'High Loss Ratio' else case when reason_for_action_taken='2' then reason_other end end end as reason_for_action_taken_desc from tbl_agencyterminated where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyMergersList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select row_number() over(order by agencymerger_id) rownum,agencymerger_id,aar_requestid,agencymerger_name,date_acquired, convert(varchar(20),date_acquired,101) as dateAcquiredFormatted,dbo.getAmountFormat(volume) as volume from tbl_agencymergers where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getCorporationPartnershipList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select row_number() over(order by corporation_partnership_details_id) rownum,name,title,ind_experience,aar_requestid, corporation_partnership_details_id from tbl_corporation_partnership_details where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getSegmentClassesList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select row_number() over(order by segment_industry_classes_id) rownum ,segment_class_name,aar_requestid,segment_industry_classes_id ,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(annual_premium as numeric(15,0))) as annual_premium,contact ,Key_contact_name,Key_contact_email from tbl_segment_industry_classes s where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getProgramBusinessList
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select row_number() over(order by program_business_id) rownum,aar_requestid,program_business_id,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(premium as numeric(15,0))) as premium,program_name,segment_class_name as segment_class_name1,product_lines,mga_mgu from tbl_program_business where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyCurrentMarketInfoRecord
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(total_annual_revenue as numeric(15,0))) as total_annual_revenue,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(commercial_premium as numeric(15,0))) as commercial_premium,cast(percentage_premium_standard as numeric(5,2)) as percentage_premium_standard,cast(percentage_speciality_lines as numeric(5,2)) as percentage_speciality_lines,total_commercial_carriers,surplus_license_holder,case when isnull(is_current_business_written_exist,0)=0 then 'No' else 'Yes' end as is_current_business_written_exist_pdf,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(agency_profitiblity_last_3years as numeric(15,0))) as agency_profitiblity_last_3years,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(agent_market_monoline_auto_n_worker_comp as numeric(15,0))) as agent_market_monoline_auto_n_worker_comp,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(agent_market_worker_comp as numeric(15,0))) as agent_market_worker_comp,agent_growth_rate_last_3years,agent_growth_rate_last_3years_yr2,agent_growth_rate_last_3years_yr3 from tbl_agency_current_market_informations where aar_requestid=#aar_requestid#

databaseoperation.name: getAgencyCurrentMarketInfoRecord
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(total_annual_revenue as numeric(15,0))) as total_annual_revenue,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(commercial_premium as numeric(15,0))) as commercial_premium,cast(percentage_premium_standard as numeric(5,2)) as percentage_premium_standard,cast(percentage_speciality_lines as numeric(5,2)) as percentage_speciality_lines,total_commercial_carriers,surplus_license_holder,case when isnull(is_current_business_written_exist,0)=0 then 'No' else 'Yes' end as is_current_business_written_exist_pdf,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(agency_profitiblity_last_3years as numeric(15,0))) as agency_profitiblity_last_3years,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(agent_market_monoline_auto_n_worker_comp as numeric(15,0))) as agent_market_monoline_auto_n_worker_comp,dbo.getAmountFormat(cast(agent_market_worker_comp as numeric(15,0))) as agent_market_worker_comp,agent_growth_rate_last_3years,agent_growth_rate_last_3years_yr2,agent_growth_rate_last_3years_yr3 from tbl_agency_current_market_informations where aar_requestid==#aar_requestid#
